1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 29]

2
00:01:22,785 --> 00:01:24,864
Having seen so many brides as a wedding matron,

3
00:01:25,225 --> 00:01:25,984
Ms. Ye,

4
00:01:25,985 --> 00:01:27,624
you're the most beautiful one.

5
00:01:28,505 --> 00:01:29,704
When the groom arrives later,

6
00:01:29,905 --> 00:01:30,904
he won't be able to help but

7
00:01:30,905 --> 00:01:32,144
be captivated at first sight.

8
00:01:38,145 --> 00:01:39,584
How long until the auspicious time?

9
00:01:42,225 --> 00:01:43,304
The auspicious time hasn't arrived yet.

10
00:01:43,505 --> 00:01:44,584
Why set off firecrackers?

11
00:01:44,785 --> 00:01:45,424
Ms. Ye,

12
00:01:45,425 --> 00:01:46,344
please wait a moment.

13
00:02:02,985 --> 00:02:03,904
Don't move.

14
00:02:25,145 --> 00:02:26,944
Marshal Lu won't let this go easily.

15
00:02:27,465 --> 00:02:28,664
Tell Zhou Yimo to be careful.

16
00:02:30,265 --> 00:02:31,984
Marshal Lu really came for revenge.

17
00:02:34,665 --> 00:02:35,464
Where's Ye Zhiqiu?

18
00:02:36,665 --> 00:02:37,624
The bride was

19
00:02:38,145 --> 00:02:40,264
taken by Marshal Lu.

20
00:02:41,865 --> 00:02:42,264
Get her to the hospital.

21
00:02:42,265 --> 00:02:42,784
Get her to the hospital.

22
00:02:43,825 --> 00:02:44,704
Yu Shi'an,

23
00:02:45,305 --> 00:02:46,784
Zhiqiu was taken by Lu Huaigu.

24
00:02:46,825 --> 00:02:47,504
I know.

25
00:02:47,905 --> 00:02:49,264
But the Marshal's mansion is heavily guarded.

26
00:02:49,385 --> 00:02:50,464
We need a solid plan.

27
00:02:51,185 --> 00:02:52,024
I'll go with you.

28
00:02:52,465 --> 00:02:53,184
Without Xiaoman,

29
00:02:54,745 --> 00:02:55,664
I wouldn't want to live either.

30
00:03:30,545 --> 00:03:31,704
Dye workshop?

31
00:03:32,665 --> 00:03:34,304
Zhou dares to confront the Marshal?

32
00:03:34,665 --> 00:03:35,584
He'll walk in upright

33
00:03:35,745 --> 00:03:36,504
and come out in a box.

34
00:03:36,945 --> 00:03:37,784
Perfect timing then.

35
00:03:37,945 --> 00:03:38,424
We'll get to

36
00:03:38,425 --> 00:03:40,024
drink Lieutenant Yu's wedding wine.

37
00:03:41,185 --> 00:03:42,184
It's Yu Shi'an.

38
00:04:02,865 --> 00:04:03,584
Get out!

39
00:04:10,705 --> 00:04:11,584
Zhou Yimo,

40
00:04:12,025 --> 00:04:13,184
please be safe.

41
00:04:39,945 --> 00:04:40,704
Everyone move aside!

42
00:04:44,945 --> 00:04:45,944
Where exactly

43
00:04:46,825 --> 00:04:47,784
is Zhou Yimo?

44
00:04:48,825 --> 00:04:49,744
Lower your guns!

45
00:04:56,505 --> 00:04:57,144
Xiaoman!

46
00:04:58,065 --> 00:04:58,904
Zhou Yimo is...

47
00:05:16,945 --> 00:05:17,544
Xiaoman,

48
00:05:18,385 --> 00:05:19,384
Marshal Lu

49
00:05:20,545 --> 00:05:21,664
was killed by Zhou Yimo.

50
00:05:22,465 --> 00:05:24,064
He's been arrested by the police.

51
00:05:24,785 --> 00:05:25,504
But don't worry,

52
00:05:26,105 --> 00:05:26,984
I'll help you.

53
00:05:35,905 --> 00:05:37,544
You kidnapped me on my wedding day,

54
00:05:38,665 --> 00:05:40,024
framed Marshal Lu,

55
00:05:41,985 --> 00:05:43,864
provoked Zhou Yimo to throw away his life,

56
00:05:44,705 --> 00:05:46,784
and used him to kill Marshal Lu.

57
00:05:47,545 --> 00:05:48,224
Yu Shi'an,

58
00:05:49,145 --> 00:05:50,504
you've played an elaborate game.

59
00:05:53,065 --> 00:05:54,784
You killed Marshal Lu, didn't you?

60
00:06:01,745 --> 00:06:02,464
Xiaoman...

61
00:06:05,585 --> 00:06:06,864
You're still as clever as ever.

62
00:06:08,985 --> 00:06:09,944
Where is Ye Zhiqiu?

63
00:06:13,865 --> 00:06:14,664
Zhou Yimo,

64
00:06:14,785 --> 00:06:15,904
who gave you the nerve

65
00:06:15,945 --> 00:06:17,344
to cause trouble in my mansion?

66
00:06:17,345 --> 00:06:18,544
I asked where Ye Zhiqiu is!

67
00:06:21,225 --> 00:06:22,344
Who is Ye Zhiqiu?

68
00:06:41,745 --> 00:06:42,704
Zhou Yimo,

69
00:06:42,945 --> 00:06:44,624
you've got some nerve!

70
00:06:44,985 --> 00:06:46,184
Not are you only smuggling opium,

71
00:06:46,545 --> 00:06:48,104
but now you've killed the Marshal!

72
00:06:48,625 --> 00:06:49,464
Take him away!

73
00:06:53,545 --> 00:06:54,104
Marshal Yu,

74
00:06:54,545 --> 00:06:55,144
from now on,

75
00:06:55,785 --> 00:06:56,544
I'm following you.

76
00:06:56,585 --> 00:06:57,184
Marshal Yu!

77
00:06:57,385 --> 00:06:58,384
From now on, we are all your soldiers.

78
00:06:58,665 --> 00:07:03,464
Marshal Yu!

79
00:07:11,305 --> 00:07:11,824
Yu Shi'an!

80
00:07:12,185 --> 00:07:12,784
Yu Shi'an!

81
00:07:13,305 --> 00:07:14,624
Why have you become like this?

82
00:07:14,945 --> 00:07:15,984
This is how I've always been.

83
00:07:17,985 --> 00:07:19,584
I just don't want to pretend anymore.

84
00:07:20,785 --> 00:07:21,464
Since no matter what I do,

85
00:07:21,465 --> 00:07:22,584
you won't like me anyway.

86
00:07:25,585 --> 00:07:27,344
I might as well be myself again.

87
00:07:30,465 --> 00:07:31,224
Take her inside.

88
00:07:33,625 --> 00:07:34,504
Yu Shi'an!
- Go.

89
00:07:54,665 --> 00:07:55,744
I know in your heart,

90
00:07:56,065 --> 00:07:56,984
there's only Zhou Yimo.

91
00:07:59,305 --> 00:08:00,224
But that's okay.

92
00:08:02,105 --> 00:08:03,304
As long as you marry me,

93
00:08:05,065 --> 00:08:06,104
I'll let him go.

94
00:08:06,825 --> 00:08:07,424
Really.

95
00:08:08,585 --> 00:08:09,784
As long as you stay by my side,

96
00:08:11,025 --> 00:08:12,064
I'll listen to everything you say.

97
00:08:19,185 --> 00:08:20,064
I agree.

98
00:08:23,505 --> 00:08:24,424
But before that,

99
00:08:27,145 --> 00:08:28,584
I want to see Zhou Yimo once.

100
00:08:43,985 --> 00:08:45,144
My dear Xiaoman.

101
00:08:47,785 --> 00:08:49,304
What trick are you playing now?

102
00:08:52,425 --> 00:08:53,704
What trick could I play?

103
00:08:56,545 --> 00:08:57,704
Since I'm going to marry you,

104
00:08:59,825 --> 00:09:00,744
I naturally need to say

105
00:09:00,745 --> 00:09:01,824
some heartless words to him

106
00:09:01,825 --> 00:09:02,824
to make him give up.

107
00:09:04,305 --> 00:09:05,064
Shi'an.

108
00:09:06,785 --> 00:09:08,704
This police station dungeon is heavily guarded.

109
00:09:09,185 --> 00:09:10,664
Under your strict supervision,

110
00:09:12,225 --> 00:09:13,424
what else could I do?

111
00:09:18,465 --> 00:09:20,184
Shi'an.

112
00:09:33,705 --> 00:09:35,264
Ever since we were kids, it's been like this.

113
00:09:38,025 --> 00:09:39,504
Whenever you call me Shi'an,

114
00:09:41,385 --> 00:09:42,704
my heart melts.

115
00:09:45,785 --> 00:09:46,664
Whatever you want,

116
00:09:47,705 --> 00:09:48,824
I can give it to you.

117
00:09:56,185 --> 00:09:57,824
But don't disappoint me.

118
00:09:59,265 --> 00:09:59,904
Understand?

119
00:10:01,705 --> 00:10:03,584
Because if you disappoint me,

120
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:06,304
I will tie Zhou Yimo up

121
00:10:07,305 --> 00:10:09,264
and make him watch our wedding night.

122
00:10:09,985 --> 00:10:11,784
Then I'll strap a bomb to him

123
00:10:12,545 --> 00:10:14,144
and blow him to bits,

124
00:10:15,825 --> 00:10:17,184
utterly pulverized.

125
00:10:32,065 --> 00:10:32,824
This is the fried rice

126
00:10:32,825 --> 00:10:34,104
you loved most as a child.

127
00:10:38,025 --> 00:10:39,344
You haven't eaten for days.

128
00:10:39,705 --> 00:10:40,624
You must be hungry.

129
00:10:41,265 --> 00:10:41,664
Here.

130
00:10:41,905 --> 00:10:42,504
Let me feed you.

131
00:10:44,625 --> 00:10:45,224
Here.

132
00:11:39,545 --> 00:11:40,384
One more bite.

133
00:11:56,425 --> 00:11:58,144
Why are you looking at me like that?

134
00:12:03,065 --> 00:12:04,064
You're thirsty, right?

135
00:12:12,065 --> 00:12:12,704
Drink.

136
00:12:20,185 --> 00:12:20,824
Again.

137
00:12:56,185 --> 00:12:56,784
Zhiqiu.

138
00:13:01,025 --> 00:13:01,704
Let go!

139
00:13:06,705 --> 00:13:07,664
Madam.

140
00:13:08,305 --> 00:13:08,944
You go out first.

141
00:13:10,905 --> 00:13:12,144
Is my order not good enough?

142
00:13:12,425 --> 00:13:13,224
No, no.

143
00:13:13,545 --> 00:13:14,704
The Marshal told me to watch...

144
00:13:15,865 --> 00:13:17,264
to protect you.

145
00:13:18,505 --> 00:13:19,544
I'll put in a good word for you

146
00:13:19,545 --> 00:13:20,664
in front of him later.

147
00:13:21,065 --> 00:13:21,904
Okay.

148
00:13:22,545 --> 00:13:22,944
I won't disturb.

149
00:13:22,945 --> 00:13:24,144
I won't disturb anymore.

150
00:13:27,265 --> 00:13:27,664
He...

151
00:13:28,065 --> 00:13:29,264
He called you Madam.

152
00:13:32,065 --> 00:13:32,544
I...

153
00:13:42,185 --> 00:13:42,584
I...

154
00:13:43,145 --> 00:13:44,784
agreed to marry Yu Shi'an

155
00:13:47,425 --> 00:13:48,504
in exchange for your freedom.

156
00:13:57,105 --> 00:13:57,744
Zhiqiu.

157
00:14:01,505 --> 00:14:02,664
I don't want you to marry him.

158
00:14:10,545 --> 00:14:11,304
Without you...

159
00:14:13,425 --> 00:14:14,424
I can't live.

160
00:14:16,265 --> 00:14:17,024
I beg you.

161
00:14:18,065 --> 00:14:18,784
No.

162
00:14:19,785 --> 00:14:20,464
No.

163
00:14:20,945 --> 00:14:21,624
I'm begging you.

164
00:14:56,385 --> 00:14:57,184
No.

165
00:14:58,705 --> 00:14:59,664
Please.

166
00:15:03,545 --> 00:15:04,384
Zhou Yimo.

167
00:15:07,145 --> 00:15:08,104
You must remember.

168
00:15:10,505 --> 00:15:11,544
If you die...

169
00:15:12,705 --> 00:15:13,904
I won't live on alone.

170
00:15:17,545 --> 00:15:18,584
You must live well.
